:{{DIcon}} How have things been?
::'''Dunn:''' Impeccable timing. Captain Gepard just sent out a bulletin saying that the frequency of Fragmentum activity has noticeably diminished &mdash; all the Silvermane Guards around the restricted zone can finally take a breather.
::'''Dunn:''' I heard many officers who were stationed on the front line for long periods can finally take their leaves... A long time coming, I'd say.
::'''Dunn:''' I'm just an insignificant logistics officer. I don't claim to know why you broke into the restricted zone last time... But whatever happened, I'm guessing the cut in Fragmentum activity has an 80% chance of being directly caused by you, right?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Yeah, we're the ones who saved Belobog.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501029861-->
:::'''Dunn:''' Ha, I knew it! It seems like we all owe you a debt of gratitude for our vacations. Thanks so much!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I can't say anything specific...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501029863-->
:::'''Dunn:''' Got it, got it... Captain Gepard doesn't like us asking too much either, so let's park this topic for now.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I've never busted into a restricted zone before, and wanna give it a try.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501029865-->
:::'''Dunn:''' Uh... You're kidding, right?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_501029866-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_501029866-->
::'''Dunn:''' *sigh* If only Madam Cocolia hadn't... Hadn't needed to sacrifice herself to save Belobog. What a noble woman.
::'''Dunn:''' I hope Lady Bronya can inherit her iron will...
::<!--Custom String Trigger: ALL_TALK_END-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: ALL_TALK_END-->
